msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "What could make ya hate me so much, Gen-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Mama, do you know what my hobby is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Karaoke, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Anyone who's ever been to this bar would know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "He's been practicing his vocal work, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Whoa, I didn't know that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Aren't you glad it's been upgraded?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "I splurged on the latest model, y'know. Make sure you sing a lot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "There's no way I can sing on that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Why not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "It's way too high-tech for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Ah, come to think of it, Gen-san hasn't sung lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "But didn't you enjoy listening to other people singing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Well sure, I like listening just as much as I like singing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "The thing sounds great. I can tell it's a great machine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Then sing already. Why waste those lungs?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Relax, Mama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "There's no way I could use such a fancy machine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "It's even got a remote control with a screen on it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "That's what makes it useful!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "It's easier to choose a song."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Yeah, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Wait, have you not even sung on the new machine once yet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "That's right. The shower is my only concert venue now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "That so...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "I can't believe your complaint is that I got a better machine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "What do you think, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Why don't you try singing on it once?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you've never even tried."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Huh? Kiryu-san, were you even paying attention?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry... What were we talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Gen-san's hating on the new machine without trying it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I just really dislike newfangled gadgets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "I only just started learning how to use cordless phones..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Gen-san, did you time travel from the past or something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Nope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Geez! I only bought it because I thought you'd use it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Now I'm gonna be in the red!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Ah, I figured money was your aim."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hey, it's still a business after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Sheesh, I don't like depending on machines for everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "It's just asking for humanity to be taken over by a robot uprising."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "The previous karaoke was a machine too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Now now, let's calm down, Gen-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Yeah, machines just take getting used to. Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Machines can be handy once you actually start using them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Yup, I agree."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Huh? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry, I was thinking about something else..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Even though it's new, I was surprised by it suddenly showing up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "So stay current. You got used to it right away, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I get pretty worked up trying to get my ranking up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "You know this bar doesn't have a whole lot of customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Shut up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Not the bar's ranking. The national ranking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "National?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "That machine instantly ranks you against others in the country."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Even though the bar is small, I can sing against lots of people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Do you guys have a problem with my bar's size...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "N-National karaoke ranking..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "That's incredible! Is that really a thing!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Why didn't you tell me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Maybe because you were whining and not listening?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "It really isn't that complicated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Umm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Let's try it, Gen-san! I sing karaoke from time to time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Yeah... I guess I'll give it a shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Yep yep, you'll figure it out in no time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "By the way, what type of songs do you sing, Gen-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "You used to sing a lot of enka, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Well, I like enka, but I want to sing this one song right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Which song?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "It's called \"Today is a Diamond.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Wait, you actually like pop music!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "I've never heard of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I listen to pop songs now and then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "It's been stuck in my head ever since I heard it on the radio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Does that karaoke machine have \"Today is a Diamond\" in it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Of course it does! I just sang it yesterday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "All right, then I'm gonna give it a go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Let's teach you karaoke and take on Japan with \"Today is a Diamond\"!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "OH!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "But then, something about using a new machine..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "I'd probably make it explode if I used it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "It's not going to explode."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "I'm sure I'll be fine once I start using it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "But I'll give it a try when I'm in the mood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Thanks..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "(That was a rather dull ending...)"
msgstr ""

